catuḥhūṃkārarūpacaturānandacaturdhyānarūpeṇa oḍiyāna-jālandhara-pullīramalaya-marusañcārād bajrahūṃkārahūṃkṛtiḥ||5|| 
vajrabāṇāyudhadharo vajrakhaḍgo nikṛntanaḥ | 
viśvavajradharo vajī ekavatrī raṇajahaḥ ||6|| vajrabāṇeti | avadhūtībāṇavajreṇa nāsārandhradvayanirodhād vajamavadhūtī, tadeva bāṇāyudhaṃ taddhāraṇā vanabāṇāyudhadharaḥ| mahāsukhādhāratayā bajramadvayajñānameva khaṅgaḥ sarva kleśaniṣūdanatvādyasya sa tathā| ata eva paramavāsanāṃ nikṛntatīti nikṛntanaḥ| pañca varṇaprāṇādivāyurviśvavajram | taduktam 
pañcajñānamayaṃ śvāsaṃ pañcabhūtasvabhāvakam | niścārya yannāsāgre piṇḍarūpeṇa kalpayet || pañcavarṇamahāratnaṃ prāṇāyāma iti sthi(smatam | svamantrahṛdaye dhyātvā cittaṃ bindugataṃ nyaset || 
(gu0 ta0 18.146-148) nāsāgre sarṣapaṃ nāma prāṇāyāmasya kalpanā| prāṇāyāme sthitāḥ pañcaraśmayo buddhabhāṣitāḥ|| pañcavarṇamayaṃ śvāsaṃ prāṇāyāmasya kalpanā| nāsikāgne prayatnena bhāvayedyogavit sadā || iti | 
