śamitāśeṣa saṃkleśaḥ saṃsārārṇavapāragaḥ | 
jñānābhiṣekamukuṭaḥ samyaksaṃbuddhabhūṣaṇaḥ ||8|| . śamiteti | śamitā nirāvaraṇatāṃ nītā aśeṣāḥ savāsanāḥ saṃpaleśā avidyā didvādaśāṅgāni yena sa tathā, pañcakāmavaśīkṛtaḥ| pañcopādānaskandhāḥ saṃsāraḥ, sa evārṇava: rāgādivyākulatvāta, tasya pāraṃ nirāvaraṇaskandhādipratilambhastatra gacchatīti saṃsārārṇavapāragaḥ| jñānaṃ caturthānandarūpama, tadevābhiṣicyate nirāvaraṇīkriyate skandhadhātvādikamanenetyabhiṣekaścaturtho bindussa eva bindubhūṣaṇamasya sa tathā, samyak saṃbuddhān vā bhūṣayatīti tathā| anena caturthābhiṣekarūpo bhagavān uktaḥ | uktañca 
karmamudrāprasane’pi "jñānamudrānurāgiṇe| rakṣaṇīyaṃ mahāsaaukhyaṃ bodhicittaṃ dṛḍhavrataaiḥ || anena rakṣitenaaiva buddhatvamiha janmani | śīlasambhārasampūrṇa puṇyajñānasamanvitam || daśa pāramitāḥprāptāḥ 'sambuddhāstryadhvavartinaḥ| 
anena sarvasaṃbuddhardharmacakra pravartitam || vātaaiḥ saṃghaṭṭamānaaistaḍidanalaśikhā drāvayenmūni candra yo yo binduto’smādgalahṛdayagato nābhiguhye niruddhaḥ| bindoḥ spandadravaṃ yat kuliśamaṇigataṃ sanniruddhaṃ dhvajāne prajñā jñānakṣaṇaṃ tadyadi dadati sukhaṃ bindu mālācyutena || 
