āryamañjuśrīnāmasaṅgītiḥ śannācyaḥ pittadhātuprakopikāḥ| nābhaau catuḥṣaṣṭināḍyaḥ, guhyakamalasya bāhyaparimaṇḍale ṣoḍaśa | etā aśītināḍyo vāyudhātuprakopikāḥ| 'asyaaiva madhyaparimaṇḍale daśa, garbhaparimaṇḍale ṣaṭ, yathāsaṃkhyaṃ sannipātaprakopikāḥ| ṣaṭcakranirodhasvabhāvaḥ| evaṃ ṣaṭpañcāśadadhikaśatanākhyo bālānāṃ mṛtyudāyikāḥ| yogināṃ sukhadāyikāḥ| ṣaṭkula nāḍībhiḥ sārddhadvāṣaṣṭyadhikaśatanāḍyaḥ | etāsu ca nāḍīṣu pratyekanāḍyo daśavāyupracāreṇa skatvadhātudaśasvabhāvena daśadhā bhavanti | evaṃ sarva daśaguṇitā viṃśatyadhikaṣoḍaśaśata saṃkhyā bhavanti| saptaviṃśatinakṣatraghaṭikāvāhinyaḥ| etannirodhāt śrīmānnakṣatramaṇḍala iti| daśadiśā vyomaprabhāsvaratvaṃ tasya sphūṭībhāvena paryantaḥ paramārthabindurūpaḥ, sa evaṃ dharmadhvajamahocchyo brahmasthānaṃ gatatvena yasya sa tathā || 28 || 
