dhīśṛṅgāradharaḥ śrīmān vīrabībhatsarūpadhṛk ||2|| kleśasaṃgrāmeti| sarvasattvacaritakleśānāṃ samyagjñānaśastreṇa nikṛntanāt | kleśasaṃgrāme eko’dvitīyaḥ śūraḥ| ārṣatvādanyathāśabdavinyāsaḥ| ajñānaṃ avidyā saaiva ripuścyutiḥ duḥkhadāyitvāt tasya do vahivikṣepaḥ, tannirābhāsīkaraṇāvajñānaripu pahā | cittamātrasyāpi nirasanenāpagatakleśopakleśatvād ghoḥ| dharmatā saṅketena bhṛṅgāraḥ sahajānandaśukrastabāraṇāttathā| uṣṇīṣāducchalitabodhicittadhārayā sarvāṅgā pyāyanena laaukikalokottarasampattimān śrīmān | upāyasya 'karuṇāṅgatvena vīrarasatvaṃ prajñāyāḥ śūnyatāṅgatvena bobhatsarasatvaṃ tadvaaidharūpaṃ mahāsukhavīrabībhatsarūpaṃ taddharatīti tathā ||2|| 
