āṇāṃ sarvākāranirāvaraṇaśūnyatā| madhyānāhatacihnasyādhastāt śavargātmakaṃ śakāravyañjanamanuccārya ṣaṣṭhaṃ binduśūnyamiti | evaṃ binduśūnyaḥ ṣaḍakṣaro dharmodayaḥ | kuliśadhara ekāraḥ śūnyatā sālambā pratisenāsvarūpiṇīti | etena pañcākṣaro mahā śūnyaḥ | svarasamūhaḥ [śukra] candra ityucyate| binduśūnyaḥ ṣaḍakṣaro vyañjanasamūho rajaḥ sūrya ityucyate | atra ca śukra candro vaṃkāro vacaṃ, rajaḥ sūrya ekāraḥ padmam, anayorvajra padmayorekatvaṃ vajra sattva iti | vacaṃ paramasukhaṃ, jñānaṃ śukra, 'sattvaḥ sarvākāraprajñābimba jñeyamiti | jñānavijñānādhiṣṭhitaṃ nirāvaraṇamekalolī bhūtatvaṃ jagadarthakārī vanasattva iti | etacca vimalaprabhāyām ( bhāga-1, pṛ0 47-50 ) uktaṃ jñeyamiti ||2|| 
