daśadigviśvanirmāṇo yathāvajjagadarthakṛt ||5|| nirmāṇakāyeti | anābhogabahirjagadarthanānāprakṛtiko nirmāṇakāya evānyeṣāṃ nirmāṇānāṃ madhye’nyo nirmāṇakāyakāyārayaḥ | sarvabhāvasahitatrikulapañcakulādivaṃ. śasya prabhāsvaratvena dhāraṇāttathā | daśadikṣu viśvasya nirmāṇaspharaṇaṃ yasya sa tathā| yathā[vata svajagadarthakaraṇād yathāvajjagadarthakṛta ||5|| 
devātidevo 'devendraḥ surendro dānavādhipaḥ | 
amarendraḥ suraguruḥ pramathaḥ pramatheśvaraḥ ||6|| devātideveti | mahārāgātmakakāyatvena brahmātmakatvād devātidevaḥ | prabhāsvara cittavajatvena viṣṇusvabhāvatvād devendraḥ| ratnāntaruṣṇīṣagamanena balirūpatvāt surendraḥ | anupamādvayaśrīdharmāmṛtalābhena rāhusvabhāvatvād dānavādhipaḥ | 'naairātmye airāvatagatitvena purandarasvabhāvatvādamarendraḥ| niḥsvabhāvī (vi)sarvadharmaprakāśanena bṛhaspatisvabhāvatvāt suraguruḥ | mahāsukhaśukradāntavaśīkṛtaprādeśikakṣaṇā(skandhā)divighnagaṇatvena vighnādhi patvātpramathaḥ| kāyavāñcittamuktirūpatryambakasvabhāvatvāt pramayeśvaraḥ ||6|| 
uttīrṇabhavakāntāra 'ekaḥ śāstā jagadguruḥ | 'prakhyātadaśadigloko dharmadānapatirmahān ||7|| uttīrṇabhaveti| sarvasattvānāṃ samyagjñānapravartakatvena uttīrṇabhavakāntāraḥ | eko’dvitīyaḥ| śāstā nānāduḥkhaduḥkhitānāṃ mahā sukhodayaśāsanāt | sarvaprapañcopa śamenāvicalitasukhajñānavihāritvājjagadguruḥ | prakhyātā daśadikṣu puṇyasaṃbhārādinā prasiddhā lokā bodhisattvādayasteṣu sambhogakāyādipratibhāsatayā dharmavānapatiḥ | mahān sthiracalātmakatvena vyāpī ||7|| 
maaitrīsannāhasannaddhaḥ . karuṇāvarmavarmitaḥ | 
prajñā khaḍgo dhanurbāṇaḥ kleśajñānaraṇajahaḥ ||8|| maaitrīti | sahajānandasurkha [citta] maaitrī saaiva sarvāṅgavyāpanāt sannāhastena sannaddho nicitaḥ cittavikṣepāpanayanāt | pūrvoktakaruṇāvarmaṇā mito rakṣitaḥ | vaaimalyagatamahā mudrā prajñā saaiva khaḍno yasya sa tathā| dhanurnādo bāṇo bindustadadvaaitarūpatvāttathā | mahārāga samādhiyogāccyuti vāsanābhakṣaṇāt kleśajñānaraṇajahaḥ || 8|| . 
