iti prathamacakrasyeyamanuśaṃsā ekādaśa padāni || 
punara paramiyaṃ vajrapāṇe vajradhara nāmasaṅgītiḥ supariśuddhā, paryavadātā, sarvajñajñānakāyavāṅmanoguhyabhūtā, sarvatathāgatānāṃ buddhabodhiḥ, samyaksaṃbuddhānāmabhisamayaḥ, sarvatathāgatānāmanuttaraḥ, dharmadhātugatiḥ sugatānām, sarvamārabala parājayo jinānām, daśabalabalitā sarvadaśa balānām, sarvajñatā sarvajñajñānānām, āgamaḥ sarvadharmāṇām, samudāgamaḥ sarva buddhadharmāṇām, vimalasupariśuddhapuṇyajñānasaṃbhārapari pūrī sarvamahābodhi sattvānām, prasūtiḥ sarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhānām, kṣetraṃ sarvadevamanuṣyasampattaḥ, pratiṣṭhā mahāyānasya, saṃbhavo bodhisattvacaryāyāḥ, niṣṭhā samyagāryamārgasya 'nikaṣo vimuktīnām, utpatti nirvāṇamārgasya, "anucchedastathāgatavaṃśasya, pravṛddhimahābodhi"sattvakulagotrasya, "nigrahaḥ sarvaparapravādinām, vidhvaṃsanaṃ sarvatīpikānām, parājayaścaturmārabalacamū senāyāḥ, saṃgrahaḥ sarvasattvā nām, āryamārga paripākaḥ sarvaniryāṇayāyinām, samādhiścatubrahmavihāra 
vihāriṇām, dhyānamekāgracittānām, yoga: kāyavāṅmano’bhiyuktānām visaṃyogaḥ sarvasaṃyojanānām, prahāṇaṃ sarvakleśopakleśānām, 'vyupaśamaḥ sarvāvaraṇānām, vimuktiḥ sarvabandhanānām, mokṣaḥ sarvopadhīnām, śāntiḥ sarvacittopaplavānām, ākaraḥ sarvasampattīnām, parihāṇiḥ sarva vipattīnām, 'pidhānaṃ sarvāpāyadvārāṇām, satpatho 'vimuktipurasya, apravṛttiḥ saṃsāracakrasya, pravartanaṃ dharmacakrasya, ucchitacchatradhvaja patākā tathāgataśāsanasya, adhiṣṭhānaṃ sarvadharma deśanāyāḥ, kṣiprasiddhimantramukhacaryā cāriṇāṃ bodhisattvānām, bhāvanādhigamaḥ prajñāpāramitābhiyuktānāṃ, bodhisattvānām, śūnyatāprati vedho’dvayaprati vedabhāvanābhiyuktānām, niṣpattiḥ sarvapāramitāsaṃbhārasya, pariśuddhiḥ sarvabhūmipāramitā"pari pūryāṇām, prativedhaḥ samyakcaturāryasatyānām, sarvadharmaaikacittaprativedhaścatu: smṛtyupasthānānām, "yāvacchandaparisamāptiḥ sarvabuddhaguṇānāmiyaṃ nāmasaṅgītiḥ| 
