103 sakalaparisamāptāmanyūnāmakhaṇḍāmebhireva gāthāpadavyañjanaḥ pratyahaṃ trikālaṃ dhārayiṣyati, vācayiṣyati, paryavāpsyati, yoniśaśca manasi kariṣyati, parebhyaśca vistareṇa 'yathāsamayaṃ yathāvatsaṃprakāśayiṣyati, pratyekaṃ cānyatamānyatamaṃ nāmārthaṃ mañjuśrījñānakāyamālambanīkṛtya ekāna manasā bhāvayiṣyati, adhimuktitattvamanaskārābhyāṃ samanta mukhavihāra vihārī sarvadharmaprativedhikayā paramayā anāvilayā prajñāviddhayā śraddhayā samanvāgataḥ san tasya tryadhvābaddhasaṃginaḥ sarvabuddhabodhisattvāḥ | saṃgamya samāgamya sarvadharmamukhānyupadarśayiṣyanti, ātmabhāvaṃ copadarśayiṣyanti, sarvabuddhabodhisattvādhiṣṭhānaṃ ca sarvakāyavāṅmanobhistasya santāne 'citte samyagadhiṣṭhāsyanti, sarvabuddhabodhisattvānugraheṇa cānugrahīṣyanti, sarvadharma vaaiśāradyapratibhānaścopasaṃhariṣyanti, sarvārhacchāvakapratyekabuddhāścāryadharma 'pramāṇatayātmabhāvaṃ copadarśayiṣyanti durdāntadamakāśca "mahākrodharājāno mahāvajradharādayo jaga"paritrāṇabhūtā nānānirmāṇakāryarojobalaṃ tejo’pra dhṛṣyatāṃ sarvamantramudrābhisamayamaṇḍalānyu"pasaṃhariṣyanti, aśeṣāśca mantramahā vidyārājyaḥ sarvavighnavināyakamārāripratyaṅgirā "mahāparājitāḥ sarā trindivaṃ pratikṣaṇaṃ sarvapitheṣu rakṣāvaraṇagupti kariṣyanti, ye ca brahmendro pendrarudranārāyaṇasanatkumāramaheśvarakārtikeyamahākālanandikeśvarayamavaruṇa - kuverahāratīdaśadiglokapālāśca "te sarve satatasaṃmitaṃ rātrindivaṃ gacchatastiṣṭhataḥ śayānasya niṣaṇṇasya svapato jāgrataḥ samāhitasyāsamā hitasya ca ekākinā bahujanamadhyagatasya yāvad grāmanagaranigamajanapada rāṣṭrarājadhānīgatasya indrakīlarathyāpratolovīthīnagaradvārarājamārga catvara śṛṅgāṭakanagarāntarāpaṇapaṇyaśālāmadhyagatasya yāvacchūnyāgāragirikandara 
