āryamañjuśrīnāmasaṅgītiḥ . nadīvanagahanopagatasya ucchiṣṭasyānucchiṣṭasya mattasya pramattasya'sadā sarvathā rakṣāvaraṇagupti kariṣyanti, rātrindivaṃ ca paraṃ svastyayanaṃ kariṣyanti, ye cānye devanāgayakṣagandharvāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragamanuṣyāmanuṣyā ye cānye grahanakṣatragaṇapatayo yāśca saptamātaro yāśca yakṣiṇīrākṣasīpiśācyastāḥ sarvāḥ sahitāḥ samagrāḥ sasaainyāḥ saparivārāḥ sarveryāpatheṣu parāṃ rakṣāvaraṇa guptiṃ kariṣyanti, paraṃ ca tasya kāye ojobalaṃ prakṣepsyanti ārogyamāyu 
vṛddhi copasaṃhariṣyanti | 
iti caturthacakrasyeyamanuśaṃsā padānyekonaviṃśatiḥ | .. punaraparaṃ vajrapāṇe vajradhara ya imāṃ nāmasaṅgīti nāmacūḍāmaṇi pratyahamakhaṇḍasamādhānatasvikṛtvā kaṇṭhagatāmāvartayiṣyati, pustakagatāṃ vā paṭhamānaḥ pravartayiṣyati, bhagavato mañjuśrījñānasattvasya rūpamālambayan, tadrūpamanucintayan tadrūpamanuvyāyan tameva rūpaṃ nirmāṇakāyenācirādeva vinayavaṃśamupādāya rakṣati, gaganatalagatāśca buddhabodhisattvāḥ nānā nirmāṇarūpakāryaḥ sahagatā rakṣanti, na ca tasya sattvasya jātu kathamapi durgatyapāyapatanaṃ bhaviṣyati, na nīcakulopapattirbhaviṣyati, na pratyanta janapadopapattirbhaviṣyati, na hīnendriyo bhaviṣyati, na mithyādṛṣṭikulo papattirbhaviṣyati, nābuddhakeṣu buddhakṣetreṣatpatsyate, na ca buddhotpādavi mukhatā taddeśitadharmavimukhaparokṣatā bhaviṣyati, na ca dīrghāyuṣkeṣu deveṣūtpasyate, na ca dubhikṣarogaśastrānta:kalpeṣutpatsyate, na ca pañcakaṣāyakāleṣūtpatsyate, na ca rājaśatrucorabhayaṃ bhaviṣyati, na sarvopakaraṇavaaikalyadāridrayabhayaṃ bhaviṣyati, nāślokābhyākhyānanindāyaśo’kīrtibhayaṃ bhaviṣyati, sujāti kulagotrasampannaśca bhaviṣyati, samantaprāsādikarūpavarṇasamanvāgataśca bhaviṣyati, priyo mana āpaḥ, paramasukhasaṃvāsaḥ, priyadarśanaśca lokānāṃ bhaviṣyati, śubhasaaubhāgyādeyavākyaśca lokānāṃ bhaviṣyati, yatra yatro 
'papatsyate, tatra tatra jātismaro bhaviṣyati, mahābhogaḥ mahāparīvāro’kṣaya parīvāraśca bhaviṣyati, agraṇīḥ sarvasattvānāmagraguṇasamanvāgato bhaviṣyati, prakṛtyā ca ṣaṭpāramitāguṇasamanvāgato bhaviṣyati, catubrahmavihāravihārī bhaviṣyati, smṛtisaṃprajanyopāyabalapraṇidhi jñānasamanvāgataśca bhaviṣyati, sarvaśāstraviśārado vāgmī ca bhaviṣyati, spaṣṭavāgajaḍaḥ paṭuśca bhaviṣyati, dakṣo’nalasaḥ saṃtuṣṭo mahārtho vitṛṣṇaśca bhaviṣyati, parama viśvāsī ca sarvasattvānāmācārya gurusaṃmataśca bhaviṣyati, aśrutapūrvāṇi ca tasya sarvaśilpakalābhijñājñānaśāstrāṇi cārthato granthataśca pratibhā samāgamiṣyanti, supariśuddhaśolājovasamudācāracārī ca bhaviṣyati, supravrajitaḥ rūpasaṃpannaśca bhaviṣyati, apramuṣitasarvajñatā bodhicittaśca bhaviṣyati, na jātu śrāvakāhatpratyekabuddhaniyamāva krāntigataśca bhaviṣyati | 
iti pañcamacakrasyeyamanuśaṃsā pādānyekapañcāśat | 
evaṃ vajrapāṇe vajradhara aprameyaguṇasamanvāgato’so mantramukhacaryā cārī bhaviṣyati, anyaaiścāprameyaairevaṃ prakāraairguṇagaṇaaiḥ samanvāgato bhaviṣyati, acirādeva vajrapāṇe vajradhara paramārthanāmasaṅgītisaṃdhārakaḥ puruṣapudgalaḥ susaṃbhṛtapuṇyajñānasaṃbhāraḥ kṣiprataraṃ buddhaguṇānsamudānīyānuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbo dhimabhisaṃbhotsyate analpakalpāparinirvāṇadharmāṇāṃ sarvasattvānāmanuttara dharmadeśako’dhiṣṭhātā daśadiksaddharmadundubhirdhamaṃgajaḥ| 
iti ṣaṣṭhacakrasyeyamanuśaṃsā prameyā| 
