upasaṃhāraḥ atha vajradharaḥ śrīmān hṛṣṭatuṣṭaḥ kṛtāñjaliḥ | praṇamya nāthaṃ saṃbuddhaṃ bhagavantaṃ tathāgatam || 1 || anyaaiśca bahubhirthirguhyendrajrapāṇibhiḥ | sa sāddhaṃ krodharājānaaiḥ provācoccaridaṃ vacaḥ || 2 || anumodāmahe nātha sādhu sādhu subhāṣitam | kṛto’smākaṃ mahānarthaḥ samyaksaṃbodhiprāpakaḥ || 3 || jagata'cāpyanāthasya vimuktiphalakākṣiṇaḥ | . śreyomārgo viśuddho’yaṃ māyājālanayoditaḥ || 4 || gambhīrodāravaaipulyo mahārtho jagadarthakṛt | buddhānāṃ viṣayo hyeṣa samyaksaṃbuddhabhāṣitaḥ || 5|| 
iti upasaṃhāragāthāḥ pañca | āryamāyājālaṣoḍaśasāhasikānmahāyogatantrāntaḥpātisamādhi jālapaṭalād bhagavatā śrīśākyamuninā bhāṣitā bhagavato mañjuśrījñāna sattvasyādvayaparamārthānāmasaṅgītiḥ parisamātā | 
